1
00:00:14,250 --> 00:00:17,310
[Always My General]

2
00:00:17,830 --> 00:00:19,990
[Episode 18]

3
00:00:26,200 --> 00:00:27,900
[Southern Yue Broken Bridge]

4
00:00:43,900 --> 00:00:44,630
Shisan.

5
00:00:45,090 --> 00:00:46,010
It's fine.

6
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:49,730
The poison has already begun to corrode my heart.

7
00:00:49,750 --> 00:00:51,000
This journey beyond the border

8
00:00:51,550 --> 00:00:53,650
may mean I'll never return to my homeland again.

9
00:00:53,680 --> 00:00:55,210
Back then, on the battlefield,

10
00:00:55,650 --> 00:00:57,390
we faced countless desperate situations.

11
00:00:57,560 --> 00:00:58,390
Each time, it was you

12
00:00:58,390 --> 00:00:59,290
who led me and our brothers

13
00:00:59,310 --> 00:01:00,630
to endure until the end.

14
00:01:00,890 --> 00:01:01,830
To us, you were the sky

15
00:01:01,930 --> 00:01:03,830
over the Jet Black Armored Cavalry.

16
00:01:05,970 --> 00:01:07,910
Now, you are the sky over Northern Zhao.

17
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:09,590
The Jet Black Armored Cavalry

18
00:01:10,300 --> 00:01:11,550
no longer exists.

19
00:01:11,740 --> 00:01:12,930
But you and I are still here.

20
00:01:13,410 --> 00:01:15,720
Vice General Xu still needs the care of the General Yunhui.

21
00:01:16,190 --> 00:01:17,120
You, Xue Shisan,

22
00:01:17,270 --> 00:01:18,860
still have my shoulder to lean on.

23
00:01:19,300 --> 00:01:20,380
When we obtain the antidote,

24
00:01:20,410 --> 00:01:22,220
I will surely take you back to our homeland,

25
00:01:22,710 --> 00:01:24,300
back to the places where we fought,

26
00:01:24,530 --> 00:01:25,880
back to the capital of Northern Zhao,

27
00:01:26,440 --> 00:01:27,660
back to Dengying Tower.

28
00:01:36,740 --> 00:01:37,610
Si,

29
00:01:38,670 --> 00:01:40,380
this is your favorite flower.

30
00:01:42,030 --> 00:01:44,200
I have always tried to protect His Highness and you.

31
00:01:45,440 --> 00:01:46,550
I never thought

32
00:01:47,810 --> 00:01:49,410
that I would still fail to fulfill my wish.

33
00:01:51,660 --> 00:01:53,070
If there is a next life,

34
00:01:54,789 --> 00:01:55,789
I

35
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,979
still wish to be your closest friend.

36
00:02:00,790 --> 00:02:02,550
How are His Highness and Shisan?

37
00:02:03,440 --> 00:02:04,800
When will they return?

38
00:02:06,130 --> 00:02:07,690
In your absence,

39
00:02:08,720 --> 00:02:09,949
Northern Zhao is in chaos.

40
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:12,230
The Eldest Prince is acting abnormally,

41
00:02:12,410 --> 00:02:13,890
the court cannot be appeased,

42
00:02:15,090 --> 00:02:16,440
and the people are suffering.

43
00:02:28,210 --> 00:02:29,740
[Market in Southern Yue]

44
00:02:35,829 --> 00:02:37,130
This is outrageous!

45
00:02:37,530 --> 00:02:39,040
The body and hair are gifts from our parents.

46
00:02:39,060 --> 00:02:39,870
How can they

47
00:02:39,870 --> 00:02:41,250
ruin their good hair like this?

48
00:02:41,670 --> 00:02:43,420
I find it rather interesting.

49
00:02:43,660 --> 00:02:44,820
Once the body and hair

50
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:45,840
are given by our parents,

51
00:02:45,860 --> 00:02:46,750
they become our own.

52
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:49,470
Why shouldn't we decide for ourselves?

53
00:02:49,770 --> 00:02:50,750
Don't you agree?

54
00:02:51,690 --> 00:02:53,030
And why these men...

55
00:02:56,930 --> 00:02:58,530
What about them?

56
00:02:58,870 --> 00:03:00,700
Women can fight on the battlefield,

57
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:02,260
and men can enjoy beauty too.

58
00:03:03,370 --> 00:03:04,680
I was ignorant.

59
00:03:04,900 --> 00:03:06,370
Clearly, General Zhou is more insightful.

60
00:03:11,870 --> 00:03:13,360
Is this your first time in Southern Yue?

61
00:03:13,380 --> 00:03:14,830
This is called fragrant hair spray.

62
00:03:14,860 --> 00:03:15,910
You spray it on your hair,

63
00:03:15,910 --> 00:03:16,870
not only does it nourish,

64
00:03:16,890 --> 00:03:17,980
but it also gives off

65
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,460
a charming floral fragrance.

66
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:22,650
It does smell pleasant.

67
00:03:28,780 --> 00:03:30,280
And this is for the eyes.

68
00:03:30,300 --> 00:03:31,110
It can change

69
00:03:31,140 --> 00:03:31,910
their color.

70
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:37,140
Eyes can change color?

71
00:03:37,160 --> 00:03:38,250
Of course!

72
00:03:38,300 --> 00:03:39,540
In Southern Yue,

73
00:03:39,570 --> 00:03:40,650
you can change

74
00:03:40,780 --> 00:03:41,840
any part of your body

75
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:43,079
whenever you like.

76
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,150
I can provide

77
00:03:44,410 --> 00:03:45,740
anything you desire.

78
00:03:46,940 --> 00:03:48,700
Anything?

79
00:03:48,810 --> 00:03:49,920
Absolutely.

80
00:03:50,310 --> 00:03:51,079
Then,

81
00:03:53,579 --> 00:03:54,420
what about poison?

82
00:03:54,930 --> 00:03:55,800
Pfft!

83
00:03:55,829 --> 00:03:57,030
Don't talk nonsense!

84
00:03:57,079 --> 00:03:58,250
This is a royal secret technique.

85
00:03:58,280 --> 00:04:00,070
How could ordinary folk like us have access to it?

86
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,900
I see you're here to stir up trouble!

87
00:04:01,930 --> 00:04:02,810
Get away!

88
00:04:04,720 --> 00:04:06,860
[Back Hall of the Southern Yue Royal Palace]

89
00:04:17,820 --> 00:04:19,550
How does Your Highness feel?

90
00:04:20,310 --> 00:04:21,959
Your Highness, are you comfortable?

91
00:04:24,490 --> 00:04:25,820
You shouldn't have broken the rules.

92
00:04:26,310 --> 00:04:27,470
Your Highness, I was wrong!

93
00:04:27,500 --> 00:04:29,210
For the sake of the years I've spent combing your hair,

94
00:04:29,230 --> 00:04:30,630
please forgive me this time.

95
00:04:30,650 --> 00:04:32,690
What a pity for such skilled hands.

96
00:04:30,810 --> 00:04:32,630
[King of Southern Yue, Zheng Linyuan]

97
00:04:32,710 --> 00:04:34,130
I've said before,

98
00:04:34,159 --> 00:04:35,480
until I find my sister,

99
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:36,390
I will never allow myself to fall in love.

100
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:37,330
But

101
00:04:37,350 --> 00:04:39,420
the Princess has been missing for many years.

102
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:41,890
Then I shall keep my vow for her all my life,

103
00:04:42,260 --> 00:04:43,190
praying for her

104
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:44,740
happiness and well-being.

105
00:04:48,140 --> 00:04:49,580
Quickly, find me

106
00:04:49,630 --> 00:04:51,780
another hairdresser to serve in the palace.

107
00:04:51,810 --> 00:04:52,850
If the new hairdresser can't do her job well either,

108
00:04:53,610 --> 00:04:54,900
there will be no need for you to live.

109
00:04:55,900 --> 00:04:56,740
Yes, Your Majesty.

110
00:04:59,950 --> 00:05:00,920
Sister,

111
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,920
where are you?

112
00:05:03,990 --> 00:05:05,560
It's been years since we parted.

113
00:05:06,030 --> 00:05:08,000
You must have grown by now.

114
00:05:08,700 --> 00:05:10,950
Shang Kefeng said you were in Northern Zhao,

115
00:05:11,530 --> 00:05:13,880
but now he has vanished without a trace.

116
00:05:14,370 --> 00:05:16,890
The spies sent have disappeared as well.

117
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:19,330
Did he find you or not?

118
00:05:19,820 --> 00:05:21,360
It seems we were right.

119
00:05:21,570 --> 00:05:22,980
To find the antidote,

120
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:24,560
we must go to the Southern Yue Royal Palace

121
00:05:24,580 --> 00:05:25,910
and seek out King Zheng Linyuan of Southern Yue.

122
00:05:27,180 --> 00:05:28,880
But given our current situation,

123
00:05:29,420 --> 00:05:30,720
how difficult will it be

124
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,290
to enter the palace?

125
00:05:36,700 --> 00:05:37,710
A decree has been issued,

126
00:05:38,290 --> 00:05:39,380
Starting today,

127
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:41,600
the entire city shall select skilled women

128
00:05:41,630 --> 00:05:42,880
to serve as royal hairdressers.

129
00:05:42,909 --> 00:05:44,460
The selection criteria are as follows.

130
00:05:44,490 --> 00:05:46,620
Unique hair buns will be favored.

131
00:05:44,909 --> 00:05:46,860
[Southern Yue Palace Head Eunuch Xi Xiang'er]

132
00:05:46,810 --> 00:05:47,830
Unusual hair accessories

133
00:05:47,850 --> 00:05:49,360
will be prioritized.

134
00:05:49,390 --> 00:05:49,870
Pick me!

135
00:05:49,900 --> 00:05:50,280
Pick me!

136
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:50,680
Pick me!

137
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:51,940
My family has been in the beauty and textile business for years.

138
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:54,300
All the women in the city have their hair buns styled by us.

139
00:05:54,330 --> 00:05:57,250
Even the technique for dyeing hair red was invented by me.

140
00:05:57,550 --> 00:05:58,770
This is our chance to enter the palace.

141
00:06:11,170 --> 00:06:12,370
She's so beautiful!

142
00:06:12,400 --> 00:06:13,510
Exactly!

143
00:06:16,620 --> 00:06:17,640
It's you.

144
00:06:17,660 --> 00:06:19,060
Come with me into the palace.

145
00:06:28,570 --> 00:06:29,360
How about this?

146
00:06:29,460 --> 00:06:30,980
Tonight, we'll split up.

147
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:32,590
You create a diversion for me in the front hall to buy time.

148
00:06:32,850 --> 00:06:34,040
After 9 p.m.,

149
00:06:34,060 --> 00:06:35,130
I will make my way

150
00:06:35,510 --> 00:06:36,780
to King Linyuan's chamber in the rear hall

151
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:37,630
to search for the antidote.

152
00:06:37,659 --> 00:06:39,040
Be extremely careful.

153
00:06:41,820 --> 00:06:43,230
You need to be careful too.

154
00:06:43,260 --> 00:06:44,060
Don't lose yourself trying

155
00:06:44,090 --> 00:06:45,090
to get close to him.

156
00:06:45,620 --> 00:06:46,960
If you feel unwell,

157
00:06:47,230 --> 00:06:48,570
we'll halt the operation immediately.

158
00:06:49,810 --> 00:06:50,780
Got it.

159
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,980
Why are you being so long-winded all of a sudden?

160
00:07:04,070 --> 00:07:05,680
I've lost too much already.

161
00:07:07,110 --> 00:07:08,560
I can't lose you too.

162
00:07:09,860 --> 00:07:10,870
Don't worry.

163
00:07:10,900 --> 00:07:12,610
The people of Northern Zhao are still waiting for us.

164
00:07:13,010 --> 00:07:14,580
I won't let anything happen to myself.

165
00:07:15,250 --> 00:07:16,160
You take care too.

166
00:07:16,190 --> 00:07:17,680
The time has come.

167
00:07:17,710 --> 00:07:20,510
Hairdresser candidates, proceed.

168
00:07:20,340 --> 00:07:21,840
[Princess Bun]

169
00:07:20,610 --> 00:07:21,970
Today, we are selecting

170
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,470
a royal hairdresser for the King.

171
00:07:23,490 --> 00:07:24,520
There will be two rounds.

172
00:07:25,290 --> 00:07:27,560
The first round tests your individual hairstyling skills.

173
00:07:27,670 --> 00:07:28,890
Those who obtain a jade token

174
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,150
will be allowed to stay.

175
00:07:52,310 --> 00:07:53,350
Silvery white like snow,

176
00:07:53,370 --> 00:07:54,430
bright as the moon,

177
00:07:54,700 --> 00:07:55,880
a truly unique hair color.

178
00:07:59,150 --> 00:08:00,280
You've passed the first round.

179
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,600
Thank you, Your Highness.

180
00:08:04,810 --> 00:08:07,380
Why does he smell like fragrant hair powder?

181
00:08:07,400 --> 00:08:08,630
Now, for the second round.

182
00:08:08,650 --> 00:08:10,030
You must style hair on-site,

183
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,530
following the diagram provided.

184
00:08:11,670 --> 00:08:13,070
The one who finishes the fastest

185
00:08:13,210 --> 00:08:15,010
will win the position

186
00:08:15,030 --> 00:08:15,910
of royal hairdresser.

187
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:19,630
Let's begin.

188
00:08:51,530 --> 00:08:52,390
I hereby announce

189
00:08:52,420 --> 00:08:54,590
the winner of today's royal hairdresser selection is

190
00:08:55,900 --> 00:08:56,650
Consort Xia.

191
00:09:07,450 --> 00:09:08,870
Don't move, King of Southern Yue!

192
00:09:09,170 --> 00:09:10,200
What are you trying to do?

193
00:09:10,370 --> 00:09:12,020
No matter how well you disguise yourself,

194
00:09:12,210 --> 00:09:14,210
you can't hide the scent of fragrant hair powder.

195
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:15,250
Everyone knows

196
00:09:15,280 --> 00:09:16,560
it's your favorite.

197
00:09:16,590 --> 00:09:17,480
What's more,

198
00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:19,090
as the Palace Head Eunuch,

199
00:09:19,110 --> 00:09:20,070
you never look to the person behind the scenes

200
00:09:20,100 --> 00:09:21,760
when making decisions.

201
00:09:21,920 --> 00:09:23,340
How long do you intend to keep up this act?

202
00:09:25,060 --> 00:09:27,650
It's said that Northern Zhao's General Yunhui is both brave and skilled in battle.

203
00:09:27,670 --> 00:09:28,700
I didn't expect you

204
00:09:28,790 --> 00:09:30,300
to also be so clever.

205
00:09:30,430 --> 00:09:31,690
Do you know who I am?

206
00:09:32,100 --> 00:09:33,690
Though Southern Yue's military strength is lacking,

207
00:09:33,790 --> 00:09:35,430
our spies are quite capable.

208
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:36,910
Since the moment you

209
00:09:36,910 --> 00:09:38,730
and Prince of Yu set foot in Southern Yue,

210
00:09:38,790 --> 00:09:40,200
I've been expecting you.

211
00:09:46,250 --> 00:09:47,060
Let him go!

212
00:09:47,090 --> 00:09:48,560
That's not the attitude of someone making a request.

213
00:09:48,580 --> 00:09:49,290
Shisan,

214
00:09:49,310 --> 00:09:50,320
let's get the antidote first.

215
00:09:50,340 --> 00:09:52,650
If you've come for the antidote,

216
00:09:52,870 --> 00:09:54,020
where's your sincerity?

217
00:10:08,450 --> 00:10:10,440
If you are willing to cooperate with me

218
00:10:10,470 --> 00:10:11,920
to capture Shang Kefeng

219
00:10:11,950 --> 00:10:14,160
and relieve the suffering of Northern Zhao's people,

220
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:17,660
I promise to forge an alliance with Southern Yue,

221
00:10:17,890 --> 00:10:19,410
never to engage in conflict again.

222
00:10:19,570 --> 00:10:21,210
Northern Zhao's military might is formidable.

223
00:10:21,260 --> 00:10:23,060
Even though the Jet Black Armored Cavalry no longer exists,

224
00:10:23,220 --> 00:10:25,450
with General Yunhui and Your Highness's influence,

225
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:27,850
you could rebuild the Jet Black Armored Cavalry in no time,

226
00:10:27,880 --> 00:10:30,160
posing a significant threat to us.

227
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:32,430
Moreover, what Your Highness's desires

228
00:10:32,460 --> 00:10:33,340
is likely more than

229
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:34,290
just this, correct?

230
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:37,270
Indeed, I have another request for Your Majesty.

231
00:10:37,990 --> 00:10:40,020
Shang Kefeng poisoned Shisan.

232
00:10:40,050 --> 00:10:41,110
Do you have a way to cure her?

233
00:10:41,770 --> 00:10:43,520
If you want me to save her, that's possible,

234
00:10:44,540 --> 00:10:46,520
but I have one condition.

235
00:10:46,560 --> 00:10:47,350
Only one of you

236
00:10:47,370 --> 00:10:48,490
can live.

237
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:59,870
It was I, Zhou Chu, who killed your 3,000 soldiers of Southern Yue.

238
00:10:59,890 --> 00:11:01,070
It has nothing to do with anyone else.

239
00:11:01,220 --> 00:11:02,910
If you are willing to perform the technique on Xu Hanzhi

240
00:11:02,930 --> 00:11:04,540
to save the innocent people of Northern Zhao,

241
00:11:04,670 --> 00:11:05,940
I am ready to die.

242
00:11:07,610 --> 00:11:08,470
No, that's not acceptable.

243
00:11:11,860 --> 00:11:13,070
Here are two cups of wine.

244
00:11:13,090 --> 00:11:14,690
One is poisoned, and the other is not.

245
00:11:14,860 --> 00:11:16,380
Leave it to fate.
